---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---
<LegalLayout
  title="Subscription Terms — Recursio"
  description="Terms for Recursio's optional auto-renewable SMART and PRO subscriptions, including billing, renewal, cancellation, and refunds."
  path="/subscription-terms"
>
  <article class="card legal">
    <h1>Subscription Terms</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Overview</h2>
    <p>Recursio offers optional auto-renewable subscriptions that unlock additional learning features.</p>
    <p>Plans:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>PRACTICE:</strong> free tier</li>
      <li><strong>SMART:</strong> paid tier with AI-assisted learning features</li>
      <li><strong>PRO:</strong> paid tier with higher limits and advanced features</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Plans</h2>
    <p><strong>SMART</strong> may include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI Writing feedback</li>
      <li>AI grammar explanations</li>
      <li>AI Coach practice</li>
      <li>more AI turns</li>
      <li>larger vocabulary capacity</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>PRO</strong> may include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>everything in SMART</li>
      <li>premium dictation voices</li>
      <li>higher AI limits</li>
      <li>deeper progress insights</li>
      <li>multiple vocabulary spaces</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Specific features and limits may evolve over time. The current set of features available on each plan is shown in the Recursio app.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Billing</h2>
    <p>
      Subscriptions are billed through the App Store or Google Play, depending on where the user subscribed.
    </p>
    <p>Prices are shown before purchase and may vary by region.</p>
    <p>Recursio does not directly process payment card information.</p>

    <h2>4. Renewal</h2>
    <p>
      Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled through the relevant app store account settings before the renewal date.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Cancellation</h2>
    <p>Users can cancel through:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Apple App Store account subscription settings</li>
      <li>Google Play subscription settings</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Canceling prevents future renewals but does not necessarily refund the current billing period.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Restore Purchases</h2>
    <p>Users can restore purchases in the Recursio app if supported by the platform.</p>

    <h2>7. Refunds</h2>
    <p>Refunds are handled by Apple or Google according to their store policies.</p>

    <h2>8. Plan Changes</h2>
    <p>
      Users may be able to upgrade, downgrade, or change billing periods through the App Store or Google Play.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Feature Changes</h2>
    <p>
      Subscription features and limits may change over time. Any material changes should be reflected in the app and these terms.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about subscriptions can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@recursio.app">support@recursio.app</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="accent-surface">
      <strong>Note:</strong> This document is a draft and should be reviewed by qualified legal counsel before publication.
    </div>
  </article>
</LegalLayout>
